---

<section class="px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-accent)]/20 bg-[var(--color-accent)]/5 px-8 py-12">
      <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)]">
        AI-Augmented Development
      </p>
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)]">
        AI와 함께 일하는 시스템이 궁금하신가요?
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-8 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        설계 → 개발 → 테스트까지, AI를 활용한 개발 워크플로우를 소개합니다.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/ai-dev"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-[var(--color-bg)] transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,255,165,0.3)]"
      >
        자세히 보기
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
